{"tid":1508621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港, 時代革命, 長期作戰, 全民抗爭!!!!!!!  (全民製作抵制名單 )","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T01:28:50.000Z","uid":260361,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5a35c87029164ccabc8a25e65797ff5f263f1357","tid":1508621,"uid":260361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:41:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n長期作戰<br />\n全民抗爭<br />\n</span></span><br />\n抗爭是廣義的，亦不是一蹴而就的。我們都要做好長期作戰的準備，今時今日港奸當道，究其原因，就是因為出賣港人只有着數沒有懲罰，故大至大財團，小至小店KOL，利欲熏心，紛紛出賣香港，拿着沾有手足鮮血的饅頭吃得津津有味；反觀撐港人的，要不被打壓排擠，要不飯碗不保。作為一個真正的香港人，絕不可以再容許這樣的情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n香港人絕對不能再金魚記憶，一定要全面抵制所有賣港賊，發揮香港人的力量，我沒有辦法阻止你出賣香港，但我絕不容許自己成為幫兇。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=bf7e028b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/</a><br />\n今日在此呼籲，全民參與編製抵制名單。讓大家舉報港奸並分門別類，同時列出出賣香港的證據，秉持既不傷及無辜，亦不有漏網之魚的精神，將港奸踢出香港。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=bf7e028b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/</a><br />\n1. 和黑警有緊密關係或黑警本身<br />\n2. 曾有賣港言行或詆毁義士<br />\n3. 曾幫助暴政打壓義民（如協助警、黑殘害義民，推行白色恐怖等）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQZVs3g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQZVs3g.png&h=51b36364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抵制名單必須提供證據才會上榜 (<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點右上角舉報</span></strong>)，所以亦希望各位手足發現港奸後馬上留下證據。香港已到了生死存亡之秋，抵制運動既可以發揮實際效果，又是100%和理非能夠全民參與，絕對是刻不容緩。我們阻止不了他們出賣良心，但我們絕對可以和喪盡良知的人割蓆。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cnopenrice.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnopenrice.com%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=bf7e028b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cnopenrice.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Hzrp3jm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzrp3jm.png&h=49482e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EOWcve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EOWcve.png&h=f02955b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8482abf46ce2246b145466c2b3ef8d270ea9b6e","tid":1508621,"uid":8232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=80eab165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e9eae4c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=1eea090c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"220dafac7959964ab42ea38aa4d6ea37af1088eb","tid":1508621,"uid":313355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f77b20d9f1dc7dd93bd20d774d4a556bff90a141","tid":1508621,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br 